5
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,470
Lou Mingyuan!

6
00:02:09,990 --> 00:02:11,400
Come down to see me.

7
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,470
It's Zeng Jiwu.

8
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:14,510
Zeng Jiwu.

9
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,220
He came here after all.

10
00:02:17,790 --> 00:02:18,790
What do you mean?

11
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,670
He's here for me.

12
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:24,860
Sir.

13
00:02:24,950 --> 00:02:26,140
Sir, please calm down.

14
00:02:26,140 --> 00:02:28,270
I'll go inform Manager Lou right away.

15
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:30,970
If something happens to me,

16
00:02:30,970 --> 00:02:31,579
remember

17
00:02:31,579 --> 00:02:33,300
to take the files on the Cherry Blossom Project with you.

18
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:34,829
The neon sign at the door needs to be replaced.

19
00:02:34,829 --> 00:02:36,260
Sundial will know once he sees it.

20
00:02:36,260 --> 00:02:37,060
It's not safe here anymore.

21
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:38,470
I'll see you at 51 Sauce Garden Lane

22
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:40,620
