She is one of us.

581
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:58,190
Go ahead.

582
00:34:58,300 --> 00:34:59,780
Mr. Ye is missing.

583
00:35:00,210 --> 00:35:01,310
What happened?

584
00:35:01,750 --> 00:35:04,150
In order to protect the students in the march,

585
00:35:04,150 --> 00:35:05,950
Mr. Ye confronted the Japanese.

586
00:35:06,040 --> 00:35:07,190
Several agents

587
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:08,630
took him away

588
00:35:08,710 --> 00:35:10,170
in the name of negotiation.

589
00:35:10,170 --> 00:35:11,060
Strangely,

590
00:35:11,190 --> 00:35:13,110
they released him in the end.

591
00:35:13,420 --> 00:35:15,540
But after that,

592
00:35:15,930 --> 00:35:18,510
he went missing.

593
00:35:18,580 --> 00:35:20,140
We searched everywhere for him,

594
00:35:20,140 --> 00:35:21,940
but we couldn't find him.

595
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:24,940
We haven't heard from him until now.

596
00:35:28,010 --> 00:35:29,530
Has the Japanese already discovered

597
00:35:29,530 --> 00:35:31,130
Secretary Chen's identity?

598
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:33,550
Qiushui.

599
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,830
I'm the one who got Mr. Ye into trouble.

600
00:35:54,100 --> 00:35:55,780
Sir, he's here.

601
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:01,670
Hello, Mr. Ye.

602
00:36:02,740 --> 00:36:03,820
Have a seat.

603
00:36:26,350 --> 00:36:27,280
Come on.

604
00:36:36,380 --> 00:36:37,420
Mr. Ye,

605
00:36:37,860 --> 00:36:40,980
we've always been respectful to men of literature and writing.

606
00:36:40,980 --> 00:36:42,350
We invited you here

607
00:36:42,830 --> 00:36:44,710
because we'd like to ask you

608
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:47,590
some questions in private.

609
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:49,270
As long as you answer,

610
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:51,390
you can go back.

611
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:05,280
Really?

612
00:37:10,490 --> 00:37:11,610
Mr. Ye,

613
00:37:12,390 --> 00:37:14,550
when did you come to Shanghai?

614
00:37:15,620 --> 00:37:16,790
What do you mean?

615
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:21,380
Recently, some communists suddenly appeared around me.

616
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:24,350
They've done something that really upsets me

617
00:37:24,460 --> 00:37:25,860
and gives me a headache.

618
00:37:27,020 --> 00:37:29,870
I got some intel and I suddenly have a feeling

619
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:32,020
that those people came to Shanghai

620
00:37:32,050 --> 00:37:33,510
at the same time as you did.

621
00:37:33,540 --> 00:37:34,580
Mr. Ye,

622
00:37:36,660 --> 00:37:38,620
do you believe in coincidences?

623
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:54,030
Mr. Ye.

624
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:56,980
Do you know this person?

625
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,310
Then this man

626
00:38:13,060 --> 00:38:15,050
should be familiar to you.

627
00:38:46,020 --> 00:38:47,210
Sir.

628
00:38:49,130 --> 00:38:50,350
Excuse me,

629
00:38:50,790 --> 00:38:52,770
where did you buy your plums?

630
00:38:53,790 --> 00:38:55,220
I'll see you at 51 Sauce Garden Lane

631
00:38:55,220 --> 00:38:56,630
in two days, at half past nine in the evening.

632
00:38:56,630 --> 00:38:57,550
Take a bag of plums with you.

633
00:38:57,550 --> 00:38:58,710
If someone asks where you bought them,

634
00:38:58,710 --> 00:39:01,450
you say you bought them in front of the Xinyue Ball Room.

635
00:39:01,450 --> 00:39:03,250
In front of the Xinyue Ball Room.

636
00:39:06,310 --> 00:39:06,800
Are they...

637
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:07,660
Are they sweet?

638
00:39:08,020 --> 00:39:09,370
If someone asks whether the plums are sweet,

639
00:39:09,370 --> 00:39:10,450
you say they're very sour.

640
00:39:10,450 --> 00:39:11,500
Very sour.

641
00:39:20,700 --> 00:39:21,960
Where is Lou Mingyuan?

642
00:39:23,620 --> 00:39:24,350
You are Sundial?

643
00:39:24,350 --> 00:39:25,450
Excuse me.

644
00:39:33,210 --> 00:39:34,300
Please enjoy.

645
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:38,150
Did something happen to him?

646
00:39:38,940 --> 00:39:39,910
He was arrested.

647
00:39:40,050 --> 00:39:41,180
You don't know that?

648
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:44,020
I...

649
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:45,300
I escaped.

650
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:47,570
I wanted to go to Lou Mingyuan that day,

651
00:39:47,610 --> 00:39:48,860
but when I went to Oz Ball Room,

652
00:39:48,860 --> 00:39:50,540
I knew something had happened when the lights were replaced.

653
00:39:50,540 --> 00:39:52,210
Because we had agreed beforehand

654
00:39:52,210 --> 00:39:53,460
that he'd change the lights

655
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:55,300
in case of special circumstances.

656
00:39:55,300 --> 00:39:56,210
I know.

657
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:58,140
I changed the light.

658
00:39:59,890 --> 00:40:01,580
Then, you are...

659
00:40:02,150 --> 00:40:03,550
What's going on with you?

660
00:40:04,270 --> 00:40:05,850
Ohashi is already looking everywhere for me.

661
00:40:05,850 --> 00:40:07,260
I couldn't steal the materials that day.

662
00:40:07,260 --> 00:40:08,030
So, I set the fire on purpose

663
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:09,490
and fled amidst the chaos.

664
00:40:09,910 --> 00:40:10,900
He has started

665
00:40:10,990 --> 00:40:12,990
to suspect that someone set the fire

666
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:16,230
and is investigating every biochemical researcher.

667
00:40:16,230 --> 00:40:18,110
I dare not go back. I can only hide.

668
00:40:20,670 --> 00:40:22,460
Have you been tailed

669
00:40:23,460 --> 00:40:25,260
when you went to the Oz Ball Room?

670
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:27,670
Lou Mingyuan taught me how to counter-stalk.

671
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:29,270
I followed his instructions

672
00:40:29,390 --> 00:40:32,460
and circled around the back door a couple of times before entering.

673
00:40:32,460 --> 00:40:34,720
I'm not the one who lured them there, am I?

674
00:40:36,730 --> 00:40:37,930
What should we do now?

675
00:40:39,020 --> 00:40:40,420
They're on to me already.

676
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:41,830
Well, I...

677
00:40:41,940 --> 00:40:44,350
I'm just an ordinary biochemical researcher. I...

678
00:40:44,350 --> 00:40:45,620
I don’t have any skills to escape,

679
00:40:45,620 --> 00:40:46,660
unlike you.

680
00:40:49,900 --> 00:40:51,150
In three days,

681
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:53,540
at 1:30 p.m.,

682
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:56,260
you go to the Shanghai Railway Station.

683
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:57,340
I'll make arrangements for you to leave.

684
00:40:57,340 --> 00:40:59,020
No, I can't leave.

685
00:40:59,310 --> 00:41:00,810
What about the Cherry Blossom Project?

686
00:41:00,810 --> 00:41:02,910
The last batch of files have been destroyed.

687
00:41:02,910 --> 00:41:05,220
I'll bring the copy with me,

688
00:41:05,830 --> 00:41:07,360
and you can take it with you.

689
00:41:08,220 --> 00:41:09,350
How come you have it?

690
00:41:09,790 --> 00:41:11,250
Lou Mingyuan has a backup?

691
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:16,160
Do you have a place to stay?

692
00:41:18,390 --> 00:41:19,100
No.

693
00:41:19,270 --> 00:41:20,820
Go to 13 Yangzi Road

694
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:22,560
and find a man named Qian San.

695
00:41:22,590 --> 00:41:23,670
Tell him

696
00:41:23,860 --> 00:41:26,020
that you are a friend of his cousin in Guangxi.

697
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:27,380
Then he will arrange accommodation for you.

698
00:41:27,380 --> 00:41:28,110
Okay.

699
00:41:28,420 --> 00:41:29,350
Thank you.

700
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:31,380
Then you are...

701
00:41:31,620 --> 00:41:33,280
If you can't tell me your name,

702
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:35,020
you can give me your code name.

703
00:41:40,100 --> 00:41:41,510
Do your job well.

704
00:41:41,660 --> 00:41:43,460
We don’t need to know each other.

705
00:41:55,490 --> 00:42:03,460
[March 1945, NBIS Chongqing Station]

706
00:42:06,120 --> 00:42:07,120
Section Chief Li,

707
00:42:07,220 --> 00:42:08,630
Captain Wei asked me to send you

708
00:42:08,630 --> 00:42:09,970
the information for 1941.

709
00:42:09,970 --> 00:42:10,770
Thank you.

710
00:42:11,930 --> 00:42:14,040
[Confidential case]

711
00:42:24,410 --> 00:42:27,140
[Confidential case]

712
00:42:29,990 --> 00:42:35,360
[Name: Lou Mingyuan; Age: 21]

713
00:42:30,780 --> 00:42:32,700
In the 20th year of the Republic of China, Lou Mingyuan

714
00:42:32,700 --> 00:42:34,140
was admitted to the Qingpu Special Training Class.

715
00:42:34,140 --> 00:42:35,420
In the 29th year of the Republic of China,

716
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:38,030
he recruited a biochemical researcher in the Cherry Blossom Project

717
00:42:38,030 --> 00:42:39,150
to be our informant.

718
00:42:38,130 --> 00:42:40,470
[Report of Undercovers in Shanghai]

719
00:42:39,290 --> 00:42:41,560
The Sundial Operation officially started.
